---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="よこそ真岡市へ">
  <main>
    <h1><span>MooKa</span>へGo!</h1>
    <span><div class="date"></div></span>
    <p>真岡市、四月の平均気温は？</p>
    <p>夜は寒いよ。長袖を持っていこう！</p>
    <div class="table">
      <table border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse">
        <tr class="graph_title">
          <td class="item">年度</td>
          <td class="item">平均気温</td>
          <td class="item">最高気温</td>
          <td class="item">最低気温</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="item">2018</td>
          <td class="temp">14.7℃</td>
          <td class="temp">30.0℃</td>
          <td class="temp">-0.1℃</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="item">2019</td>
          <td class="temp">11.4℃</td>
          <td class="temp">26.6℃</td>
          <td class="temp">-3.9℃</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="item">2020</td>
          <td class="temp">10.7℃</td>
          <td class="temp">23.7℃</td>
          <td class="temp">-1.4℃</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="item">2021</td>
          <td class="temp">12.8℃</td>
          <td class="temp">25.8℃</td>
          <td class="temp">0.5℃</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="item">2022</td>
          <td class="temp">13.7℃</td>
          <td class="temp">28.8℃</td>
          <td class="temp">-3.1℃</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
    <hr>

    <iframe
      src="https://www.appsheet.com/start/ed1dd4bf-61bf-4e6e-a0a1-519fd0ef15d8#appName=%E7%9C%9F%E5%B2%A1%E8%A8%98%E5%BF%B5%E9%A4%A8-496136311&group=%5B%5D&page=deck&sort=%5B%5D&table=%E7%9C%9F%E5%B2%A1%E8%A8%98%E5%BF%B5%E9%A4%A8&view=%E7%9C%9F%E5%B2%A1%E8%A8%98%E5%BF%B5%E9%A4%A8"
    >
    </iframe>
    <br />
    <button id="photo">写真を送ろう</button>

    <div class="twiter">
      <blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr">他では味わえない完熟いちご🍓は贈り物🎁にも最適.｡ ｡.:*･ﾟ♡★♡<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/mokafan?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#mokafan</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E3%81%84%E3%81%A1%E3%81%94%E7%8E%8B%E5%9B%BD%E6%A0%83%E6%9C%A8%E3%81%AE%E9%A6%96%E9%83%BD%E3%82%82%E3%81%8A%E3%81%8B?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#いちご王国栃木の首都もおか</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%80%E3%81%AE%E3%81%84%E3%81%A1%E3%81%94%E3%81%AE%E3%81%BE%E3%81%A1?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#日本一のいちごのまち</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E3%82%82%E3%81%8A%E3%81%8B%E3%81%97%E3%81%A8%E8%AA%AD%E3%81%BF%E3%81%BE%E3%81%99?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#もおかしと読みます</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E6%A0%83%E6%9C%A8%E7%9C%8C?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#栃木県</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E3%81%84%E3%81%A1%E3%81%94?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#いちご</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E8%B4%88%E3%82%8A%E7%89%A9?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#贈り物</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E3%83%97%E3%83%AC%E3%82%BC%E3%83%B3%E3%83%88?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#プレゼント</a> <a href="https://t.co/Cta6rpHJiz">pic.twitter.com/Cta6rpHJiz</a></p>&mdash; 真岡市 (@mokacityhall) <a href="https://twitter.com/mokacityhall/status/1641258947981070336?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 30, 2023</a></blockquote> <script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
    </div>

    <script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"
    ></script>
    <br />
    <div class="btn">
      <button id="btn">真岡市広報</button>
    </div>
    <br />
    <p>// みんな大好き<span>マヌルネコ</span>の歌 //</p>
    <video controls width="300" height="150" src="./asset/manul.mp4"></video>
    <br />


    <p><span>栃木人</span>のトリセツ</p>
    <iframe
      width="300"
      height="350"
      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yHvlItPxNX8"
      title="YouTube video player"
      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
      allowfullscreen></iframe>

	  <p>🄫2023 <a href="https://goohayami.com/">goohayami.com</a></p>
  </main>
</Layout>

<script>
  const btn = document.getElementById("btn");
  btn.addEventListener("click", () => {
    location.href =
      "https://www.city.moka.lg.jp/citypromotion/about_moka/7644.html";
  });

  const photo = document.getElementById("photo");
  photo.addEventListener("click", () => {
    location.href =
      "https://www.appsheet.com/start/ed1dd4bf-61bf-4e6e-a0a1-519fd0ef15d8#appName=%E7%9C%9F%E5%B2%A1%E8%A8%98%E5%BF%B5%E9%A4%A8-496136311&group=%5B%5D&page=deck&sort=%5B%5D&table=%E7%9C%9F%E5%B2%A1%E8%A8%98%E5%BF%B5%E9%A4%A8&view=%E7%9C%9F%E5%B2%A1%E8%A8%98%E5%BF%B5%E9%A4%A8";
  });

  // 日にちを表示
  const today = new Date();
  const date_today =
  today.getFullYear() +
  "年" +
  (today.getMonth() + 1 + "月") +
  today.getDate() +
  "日";

const date = document.querySelector(".date");
date.textContent =  date_today;


</script>

<style>
  video {
    margin: 0;
  }
  .twiter {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  iframe {
    height: 400px;
  }
  main {
    margin: 0;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;

    font-family: "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
  }
  table {
    border: 1px solid black;
  }
  .table {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    /* font-weight: 800; */
    margin: 0;
  }
  span {
    color: rgb(188, 30, 30);
  }

  .graph_title {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .item {
    padding: 0.3rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .temp {
    text-align: right;
    padding: 0.4rem;
  }

  #btn,
  #photo {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }
  .btn {
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
